{
  "id": "6a2586096239872061c5b7d0",
  "title": "5時間睡眠いける？",
  "created": 1780844045,
  "updated": 1781031679,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2586096239872061c5b7d0",
      "text": "5時間睡眠いける？",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1780844045,
      "updated": 1780879848
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25861000000000004485c7",
      "text": "[睡眠時間]か[5時間]の日は耐えられるか？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780844049,
      "updated": 1780844072
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25862800000000004485ca",
      "text": " 最近は無理だ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780844072,
      "updated": 1780844088
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25863300000000004485cb",
      "text": "  カフェインをとってやる気を出せばいけるかもしれない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1780844083,
      "updated": 1780844094
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25861200000000004485c8",
      "text": "\t無理すぎる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780844051,
      "updated": 1780872511
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25f5f80000000000c24071",
      "text": "\t\t7.5時間が最低ライン",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780872697,
      "updated": 1780872700
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25f5fd0000000000c24072",
      "text": "\t\t30分減ると露骨に認知力が落ちる感じ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780872701,
      "updated": 1780872774
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25f6100000000000c24073",
      "text": "\t\t\t擬態に費やせなくなるのが一番危ない。対人トラブルを誘発してしまう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780872720,
      "updated": 1780872767
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25f6240000000000c24074",
      "text": "\t\t\tある意味睡眠不足は命取り",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780872740,
      "updated": 1780872748
    },
    {
      "id": "6a25f53e0000000000c24070",
      "text": " むり[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1780872511,
      "updated": 1780879080
    },
    {
      "id": "6a260ef40000000000a93bf2",
      "text": "  翌日全滅する",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1780879091,
      "updated": 1780879115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a260ee40000000000a93bf1",
      "text": " 10年以上 2.5h - 3h 睡眠だったけど、ここ2, 3年は4時間くらい眠れてる[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1780879075,
      "updated": 1781031637
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2862e900000000001fca73",
      "text": " 　睡眠時間よりも眠りの深さのほうがだいじ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781031658,
      "updated": 1781031679
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28624c00000000001fca72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781031501,
      "updated": 1781031501
    }
  ]
}